name: Another walk along the "rambla"
description:
Summering from the past 

Time speeds up, takes us away from the past, for better or for worse.
But there are always traces.
It makes sense to think about it. Pause, reflect.
Slow down, slow down.
Escape the monotony of permanent novelty.
Think about what we’re abandoning.
Thinking about how we want to build our future
